  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>The original Dark Quest, fully remastered.</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A powerful sorcerer has risen in the land, building a dungeon beneath the village of Darkwood. From this stronghold, his minions raid nearby villages, spreading terror and death. A small band of heroes, led by a mighty barbarian, dares to defy the sorcerer’s power. Take control, descend into the dungeon, and put an end to the evil threatening the realm.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Control a party of up to 3 characters each with their own unique abilities: Use the unique strengths of each character and work together to defeat the minions of the evil sorcerer. Slaughter endless hordes of orcs & undead: Your strength, courage and strategy will be the key into wining every battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342860/extras/f1168bde3a7b4760cfbe4043eef45831.poster.avif?t=1769396549\" width=780 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342860/extras/f1168bde3a7b4760cfbe4043eef45831.webm?t=1769396549\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342860/extras/f1168bde3a7b4760cfbe4043eef45831.mp4?t=1769396549\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Roll the skull of fate and reveal your twisted fate: The evil sorcerer will torment your soul for his own amusement, he will summon you in the sphere of judgment where you will be forced to play a twisted game of death, and can you survive his magic?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342860/extras/1e8be995c583be50c789969d0162ddd8.poster.avif?t=1769396549\" width=780 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342860/extras/1e8be995c583be50c789969d0162ddd8.webm?t=1769396549\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342860/extras/1e8be995c583be50c789969d0162ddd8.mp4?t=1769396549\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Trade with the people in the village: Spend the gold you find in your adventures in the village to buy new potions, weapons and spells for your characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342860/extras/ec9fdf1c258a47a01ed6554ff8eff94e.poster.avif?t=1769396549\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342860/extras/ec9fdf1c258a47a01ed6554ff8eff94e.webm?t=1769396549\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342860/extras/ec9fdf1c258a47a01ed6554ff8eff94e.mp4?t=1769396549\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>The original Dark Quest, fully remastered.</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A powerful sorcerer has risen in the land, building a dungeon beneath the village of Darkwood. From this stronghold, his minions raid nearby villages, spreading terror and death. A small band of heroes, led by a mighty barbarian, dares to defy the sorcerer’s power. Take control, descend into the dungeon, and put an end to the evil threatening the realm.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Control a party of up to 3 characters each with their own unique abilities: Use the unique strengths of each character and work together to defeat the minions of the evil sorcerer. Slaughter endless hordes of orcs & undead: Your strength, courage and strategy will be the key into wining every battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342860/extras/f1168bde3a7b4760cfbe4043eef45831.poster.avif?t=1769396549\" width=780 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342860/extras/f1168bde3a7b4760cfbe4043eef45831.webm?t=1769396549\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342860/extras/f1168bde3a7b4760cfbe4043eef45831.mp4?t=1769396549\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Roll the skull of fate and reveal your twisted fate: The evil sorcerer will torment your soul for his own amusement, he will summon you in the sphere of judgment where you will be forced to play a twisted game of death, and can you survive his magic?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342860/extras/1e8be995c583be50c789969d0162ddd8.poster.avif?t=1769396549\" width=780 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342860/extras/1e8be995c583be50c789969d0162ddd8.webm?t=1769396549\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342860/extras/1e8be995c583be50c789969d0162ddd8.mp4?t=1769396549\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Trade with the people in the village: Spend the gold you find in your adventures in the village to buy new potions, weapons and spells for your characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342860/extras/ec9fdf1c258a47a01ed6554ff8eff94e.poster.avif?t=1769396549\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342860/extras/ec9fdf1c258a47a01ed6554ff8eff94e.webm?t=1769396549\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/342860/extras/ec9fdf1c258a47a01ed6554ff8eff94e.mp4?t=1769396549\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
